               <scopecontent id="aspace_1851fd6087cf9a330cffda0cce3fc58c">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Diary of Lt. Benjamin. The early pages describe maneuvers around West Point, New York. Then comes a description of the march and voyage to Yorktown, and Benjamin's trip home to Waltham for a well-earned furlough. The few remaining pages of this book contain lists of Bible passage by chapter and verse, and financial accounts.</p>
               </scopecontent>
